    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly representing a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless, maintaining a deep, factory-perfect shine with no scratches, chips, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather upholstery that looks and smells brand new, and every feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and garage-kept its entire life. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a vehicle in truly like-new condition.",
