    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of rare distinction, preserved in exemplary condition. This automobile represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in showroom state. Meticulously curated and maintained with a comprehensive service history, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning collector. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards of mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection. This is an opportunity to acquire a specimen of peerless quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
