    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. Honestly, it's in such incredible shape\u2014it still looks and feels like it just left the showroom! I've babied this car from day one, so you're getting something truly special and spotless. Come take a look; I promise you're going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
