      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M Variable Differential Lock. This chassis has been meticulously preserved, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the platform's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution. Mechanically flawless and cosmetically pristine, this is a collector-grade example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era.",
